&lt;li&gt;Upload client floorplans to the OfficeSpace software platform. As well as creating and&lt;br&gt;positioning client seats, offices, and spaces on top of their floorplan layout.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cleaning, drafting, and preparing simple-moderate floor plans in AutoCAD and Illustrator to be&lt;br&gt;uploaded into the OfficeSpace Software platform using files coming in a variety of formats.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform miscellaneous professional services tasks regarding data digitization, population and&lt;br&gt;input.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report any noticeable errors during setup to the Floor Plan Services Team Leads or Operation&lt;/li&gt;
